### Get all cryptos
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos

### Search cryptos by name
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos/search?name=Bitcoin

### Search cryptos by kind
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos/search?kind=stable

### Search cryptos by symbol
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos/search?symbol=BTC

### Search cryptos with multiple criteria
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos/search?name=Ethereum&kind=coin&symbol=ETH

### Get crypto by symbol
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos/BTC

### Get crypto rate
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos/BTC/rate

### Get non-existent crypto
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos/INVALID

### Get rate for non-existent crypto
GET http://localhost:3000/cryptos/INVALID/rate 